Bishii Febraayo 18, 2020, Boli Zhang iyo asxaabtiisa waxay daabaceen daraasad lagu barbardhigo daaweynta daaweynta reer galbeedka (WM) oo keliya daaweynta isku dhafan ee WM iyo TCM.
