Dubai, Sydney, iyo Melbourne ayaa sidoo kale lagu soo warramay inay yihiin meelo caan ah oo loogu talagalay dadka ka socda Wuhan.
Bali ayaa lagu soo warramay inay ugu yaraan awood u leedahay 20ka magaalo ee ugu caansan ee loo socdo marka la eego diyaar garowga, halka magaalooyinka Australia loo tixgeliyey kuwa ugu awooda badan. Australia waxay soo saartay Qorsheeda Jawaabta Degdegga ah ee Coronavirus-ka Cusub (COVID-19) 7ka Febraayo.
