Kanada, Mareykanka, Japan, Hindiya, Sri Lanka, Australia, Faransiiska, Argentina, Jarmalka, iyo Thailand ayaa ka mid ahaa kuwa ugu horeeya ee qorsheynaya in muwaadiniintooda laga daadgureeyo.
Pakistan ayaa sheegtay inaysan ka soo qaadi doonin muwaadiniin Shiinaha ah.
