Bishii Febraayo 14, Kooxda Howlgalka Wadajirka ah ee WHO-da ee Shiinaha ayaa la hawlgeliyey si ay u siiso khabiiro caalami ah iyo WHO ah oo ku sugan dhulka Shiinaha si ay uga caawiyaan maareynta gudaha iyo qiimeynta "dhibcaha daran iyo gudbinta cudurka" iyagoo martigelinaya aqoon isweydaarsiyo iyo kulamo lala yeesho hay'adaha muhiimka ah ee heer qaran iyo inay sameeyaan booqashooyin goobta ah si loo qiimeeyo "saameeca howlaha jawaabta ee heerka gobolka iyo gobolka, oo ay ku jiraan deegaannada magaalooyinka iyo miyiga". Bishii Febraayo 25, WHO waxay ku dhawaaqday in "dunidu ay wax badan ka qabato si loo diyaariyo cudurka faafa ee coronavirus", iyadoo sheegtay in in kastoo ay wali ay yaraa in lagu magacaabo masiibo, dalalku ay weli "heer diyaar garow ah" yihiin.
Iyada oo jawaab u ah cudur ka dhacay Iran, WHO waxay u dirtay koox howlgal wadajir ah oo halkaas ku qiimeyn doonta xaaladda. 28-kii Febraayo, saraakiisha WHO waxay sheegeen in qiimeynta halista coronavirus heer caalami ah laga kordhin doono "sare" ilaa "badanaa sare", heerka ugu sarreeya ee digniinta iyo qiimeynta halista.
