Jawaabta ka soo horjeedda waxaa ka mid ahaa codsi uu Agaasimaha Guud ee WHO Tedros Adhanom u soo jeediyay inuu iska casilayo, oo ay saxiixdeen 733,000 oo qof ilaa 6ka Abriil.
Bishii Maarso 26, 2020, tobanaan khabiir oo u qaabilsan xuquuqda aadanaha ee Qaramada Midoobay ayaa ku adkeeyay ixtiraamka xuquuqda qof kasta inta lagu jiro masiibada COVID-19.
Kooxda khubarada ayaa sheegtay in qof walba uu xaq u leeyahay tallaabooyin badbaadinaya noloshooda, dawladuna ay mas'uul ka tahay.
Kooxdu waxay carabka ku adkeysay in la'aanta kheyraadka ama caymiska caafimaadka aysan marnaba u adeegsan karin inay xaq u noqoto takoorka koox gaar ah.
Khubarada ayaa carrabka ku adkeeyay in qof walba uu xaq u leeyahay caafimaadka, oo ay ku jiraan dadka naafada ah, dadka ka tirsan kooxaha yaryar, dadka waayeelka ah, dadka guryaha ka barakacay, kuwa hoy la'aanta ah, kuwa ku nool xaaladaha aadka u liita, dadka xadhiga lagu hayo, iyo sidoo kale qaxootiga iyo kooxaha kale ee aan la qeexin ee u baahan taageero dowladeed.
Ururada dawladda caalamiga ah ayaa wax ka qabanaya saameynta dhaqaale iyo bulshada ee dhibaatada COVID-19.
Ururka iskaashiga iyo horumarinta dhaqaalaha ayaa bilaabay barxad lagu siinayo macluumaad waqti ku habboon oo dhamaystiran oo ku saabsan jawaabaha siyaasadda ee dalalka adduunka oo dhan, iyo sidoo kale aragtiyo iyo talooyin.
Laga soo bilaabo siyaasadaha lagu xoojinayo nidaamyada caafimaadka iyo dhaqaalaha adduunka ilaa wax ka qabashada saameynta xiritaanka iyo xaddidaadaha safarka, xarunta dijitaalka ah waxay ka kooban tahay Raadinta Siyaasadda Waddanka, waxayna ujeedkeedu yahay inay ka caawiso waddamada inay ka bartaan midba midka kale iyo inay fududeynayaan jawaab celinta caalamiga ah ee isku xiran ee caqabadda coronavirus.
Dowladda Shiinaha ayaa waxaa dhaliilay Mareykanka, Wasiirka Wasaaradda Boqortooyada Ingiriiska ee Michael Gove, iyo wiilkii Madaxweynaha Brazil Jair Bolsonaro Eduardo Bolsonaro, sida ay ula qabsatay cudurka faafa, kaas oo ka bilaabmay gobolka Shiinaha ee Hubei.
Qaar ka mid ah maamulayaasha heer gobol ee Xisbiga Qaramada Midoobay ee Shiinaha (CPC) ayaa laga qaaday shaqada ay ku qabteen dadaallada karantiil ee bartamaha Shiinaha, taas oo muujineysa in aysan ku qanacsanayn jawaabta hay'adda siyaasadeed ee cudurka ka dhacay gobolladaas.
Qaar ka mid ah faallo bixiyayaasha ayaa aaminsan in tallaabadan loo sameeyay si loo ilaaliyo xoghayaha guud ee Xisbiga Qaramada Midoobay ee Shiinaha Xi Jinping ka cadhada dadweynaha ee cudurka coronavirus.
Saraakiisha qaar ee Shiinaha, tusaale ahaan Zhao Lijian waxay diideen xaqiijinta hore ee cudurka faafa ee coronavirus ee ka bilaabmay Wuhan, iyagoo ku taageeraya aragtiyada shirqoolka ee ku saabsan COVID-19 oo ka yimid Mareykanka ama Talyaaniga.
Maamulka Mareykanka ee Donald Trump ayaa ku tilmaamay coronavirus "virus Shiinaha" ama "virus Wuhan" isagoo sheegay in "censorship" Shiinaha uu "ku xadgudbay fayraska hadda u noqday masiibo caalami ah", taas oo ay si kale u dhaleeceen qaar ka mid ah dhaleeceeyayaasha sida cunsuriyad iyo "la wareejiyo" maamulkiisa ku guuldareysashada inuu xakameeyo cudurka.
Daily Beast waxay heshay cable dowladda Mareykanka oo ku tilmaamaysa istaraatiijiyad isgaarsiineed oo asal ahaan ka timid Golaha Ammaanka Qaranka, iyadoo istaraatiijiyadani lagu soo xigtay "Wax walba waxay ku saabsan yihiin Shiinaha.
Waxaa la inaga sheegayaa inaan isku dayno inaan soo saarno farriintan siyaabo kasta oo suurtagal ah, oo ay ku jiraan shirar saxaafadeed iyo muuqaal telefishan. "Wararka sida Politico, Foreign Policy, iyo Bloomberg ayaa sheegtay in dadaalka Shiinaha ee ah inuu gargaar u diro dalalka uu fayraska ku dhacay uu qayb ka yahay olole olole lagu doonayo saameynta caalamiga ah.
Madaxa siyaasadda arrimaha dibadda ee Midowga Yurub Josep Borrell wuxuu ka digay in ay jirto "qayb ka mid ah geopolitikada oo ay ku jiraan halganka saameynta iyada oo loo marayo wareegga iyo 'siyaasadda deeqsi".
Borrell ayaa sidoo kale sheegay in "Shiinaha uu si adag u dhiirrigeliyo farriinta ah in, ka duwan Mareykanka, uu yahay la-hawlgalayaal mas'uul ah oo lagu kalsoonaan karo".
Shiinaha ayaa sidoo kale ugu baaqay Mareykanka inuu ka qaado cunaqabateyntiisa ku saabsan Suuriya, Venezuela iyo Iran, iyadoo la sheegay in ay caawimaad u dirto labada dal ee dambe.
