Bishii Maarso 22, kadib markii uu taleefan kula hadlay Ra'iisul Wasaaraha Talyaaniga Giuseppe Conte, madaxweynaha Ruushka Vladimir Putin wuxuu diyaariyey in ciidanka Ruushka ay u diraan Italy dhaqtarro ciidan, gawaarida jeermiska gaarka ah, iyo qalab kale oo caafimaad.
