Guddoomiyaha New York Andrew Cuomo wuxuu ku dhawaaqay in tijaabooyinka New York State ee chloroquine iyo hydroxychloroquine ay bilaaban doonaan 24-ka Maarso. 28-ka Maarso, FDA waxay oggolaatay isticmaalka hydroxychloroquine sulfate iyo chloroquine phosphate iyadoo la raacayo oggolaanshaha isticmaalka degdegga ah (EUA).
Daaweynta looma ansixin habka tijaabooyinka bukaanka ee FDA waxaana loo oggol yahay EUA kaliya daaweynta tijaabada ah ee loogu talagalay isticmaalka degdegga ah ee bukaannada isbitaalka lagu rakibay laakiin aan awoodin inay helaan daaweyn tijaabo caafimaad.
CDC waxay sheegtay in "isticmaalka, qiyaasta, ama muddada loo qaato hydroxychloroquine ee ka hortagga ama daaweynta cudurka SARS-CoV-2" aysan weli la xaqiijin.
