tallaalka COVID-19 waa tallaal qiyaasi ah oo looga hortago cudurka coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
In kasta oo aan la dhammaystirin tijaabooyinka bukaanka, haddana waxaa jira dadaallo badan oo socda si loo soo saaro tallaal noocaas ah.
Dhamaadkii Febraayo 2020, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) wuxuu sheegay inuusan filayn in tallaal looga hortago SARS-CoV-2, oo ah fayraska sababaha, uu ka heli karo wax ka yar 18 bilood.
Shan codsade oo tallaal ah ayaa ku jiray daraasadaha badbaadada ee wajiga I bishii Abriil.
COVID-19 waxaa la ogaaday bishii Diseembar 2019.
Cudurka weyn ayaa ku faafay adduunka oo dhan sanadka 2020, taas oo horseeday maalgashiyo iyo cilmi baaris aad u badan oo lagu horumarinayo tallaal.
Ururo badan ayaa isticmaalaya genomes la daabacay si ay u horumariyaan tallaallada suurtagalka ah ee ka dhanka ah SARS-CoV-2.
Bishii Abriil, waxaa lagu sheegay in shuruudaha hindisaha CEPI ee horumarinta tallaalka ay yihiin xawaaraha, awoodda wax soo saarka, hirgelinta baaxadda, iyo helitaanka caalamiga ah.
Bishii Abriil, saynisyahannada CEPI waxay soo sheegeen in 10 barnaamij oo tikniyoolajiyad kala duwan ay cilmi baarista iyo horumarinta ku jiraan bilowgii 2020 si loo abuuro tallaal wax ku ool ah oo ka dhan ah COVID-19.
Ujeeddooyinka ugu waaweyn ee barxadda ee loo horumariyey daraasadaha badbaadada ee wajiga I waxaa ka mid ah:
nucleic acid (DNA iyo RNA) (hal-abuuraha marxaladda I iyo musharaxa tallaalka: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
virus vector (Hawlaha wajiga I iyo musharaxa tallaalka: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus type 5 vector)
Sida ay soo sheegeen saynisyahannada CEPI bishii Abriil, 115 oo ah codsadayaasha tallaalka ayaa ku jira marxaladda hore ee horumarinta, 78 ayaa la xaqiijiyay inay yihiin mashaariic firfircoon (79, sida laga soo xigtay Machadka Milken), iyo 37 kale oo la shaaciyay, laakiin macluumaad yar oo dadweyne ah ayaa la heli karaa (oo la maleynayo inay qorsheynayaan ama la qorsheynayo).
Tijaabada wajiga I-II waxay qabataa baaritaano badbaado iyo difaaca immunogenicity oo hordhac ah, sida caadiga ah waa randomized, placebo-controlled, iyo goobo badan, iyadoo la go'aamiyo qiyaaso sax ah oo wax ku ool ah.
Tijaabooyinka wajiga III waxay caadi ahaan ku lug leeyihiin kaqeybgalayaal badan, oo ay ku jiraan koox xakamaynta, iyo tijaabada waxtarka tallaalka si looga hortago cudurka, iyadoo la socdo kormeerka saameynta xun ee qiyaasta ugu fiican.
79 ka mid ah Musharaxiinta tallaalka ee horumarinta firfircoon (oo la xaqiijiyay horaantii Abriil 2020), 74 wali laguma qiimeynayo bini'aadamka (waliba cilmi baarista "ka hor-cilmiga").
